oitte</span><span class=\"tb-dot\"></span><span class=\"tb-name\">Stanford</span><span class=\"tb-dot\"></span><span class=\"tb-name\">Kaiser Permanente</span><span class=\"tb-dot\"></span><span class=\"tb-name\">LexisNexis</span><span class=\"tb-dot\"></span><span class=\"tb-name\">Biogen</span><span class=\"tb-dot\"></span><span class=\"tb-name\">Danaher</span><span class=\"tb-dot\"></span><span class=\"tb-name\">Forbes</span><span class=\"tb-dot\"></span><span class=\"tb-name\">PGA</span><span class=\"tb-dot\"></span><span class=\"tb-name\">Motorola</span><span class=\"tb-dot\"></span><span class=\"tb-name\">Novo Biosciences</span><span class=\"tb-dot\"></span><span class=\"tb-name\">Microduino</span><span class=\"tb-dot\"></span></div></div>"
